  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK885">
<l>uṟaṉmuṟaiyā ṉuṭpakai tōṉṟi ṉiṟaṉmuṟaiyā </l>
<l>ṉētam palavun tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there appears internal hatred in a (king's) family; it will lead to many a fatal crime.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
